Class WarnThemeAlert

java.lang.Object
javafx.scene.control.Dialog<javafx.scene.control.ButtonType>
javafx.scene.control.Alert
com.oracle.javafx.scenebuilder.api.alert.SBAlert
com.oracle.javafx.scenebuilder.gluon.alert.WarnThemeAlert
All Implemented Interfaces:
javafx.event.EventTarget
public class WarnThemeAlert
extends SBAlert
Used when the user adds a Gluon control to the document or loads a document with a Gluon control and Gluon Mobile theme is not set. When a Gluon control is used, Gluon Mobile theme must be set in order for the control to work correctly.
